OL,3,C'Search your conscience': Mother's
OL,4,Cappeal two years on from son's murder
OL,6,FThe mother of a murdered teenager has
OL,7,Fcalled for people to stop protecting
OL,8,F"scum" with guns, as she appealed for
OL,9,Finformation on the second anniversary
OL,10,Fof his death.
OL,12,FEllis Cox, 19, was killed at the Liver
OL,13,FIndustrial Estate in Aintree,
OL,14,FLiverpool, on 23 June 2024.
OL,16,FNine people have been arrested in
OL,17,Fconnection with his death but all have
OL,18,Fbeen released on bail and police
OL,19,Fcontinue to search for his killer.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@FO]
