OL,3,C'Search your conscience': Mother's
OL,4,Cappeal two years on from son's murder
OL,6,FTwo years on from his death, his
OL,7,Fmother Carolyn Cox called for anyone
OL,8,Fwith information to "search their
OL,9,Fconscience".
OL,11,FShe said: "If it can happen to Ellis
OL,12,Fthen it can happen to anybody. They
OL,13,Fare still going to run round thinking
OL,14,Fthat they're in the movies with a gun.
OL,16,F"They're not professionals. These are
OL,17,Fjust scum, basically, with guns, so if
OL,18,Fthey've done it once they will do it
OL,19,Fagain.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@KO]sD@KOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
